config.comment.selectionBox.colorMode=Gradient animates between the block start and end colors. Solid uses the block single color setting.
config.enum.selectionBox.colorMode.GRADIENT=Gradient
config.enum.selectionBox.colorMode.SOLID=Solid

config.name.selectionBox.solidColor=Block Single Color
config.comment.selectionBox.solidColor=The block highlight color used in Solid mode.

